  Liz Hurley wowed her 2.4 million followers with her latest holiday look today. The  star wore a leopard pattern slip dress, which she hitched up as she sat on a boat looking out at the sea. Pictures from the shore showed the dress’ full length and shape as Liz posed on the sand. Promoting one of her own designs, Liz captioned the pics: “At last!! We have my favourite, silk Leopard Slip Dress in stock - it folds into nothing in your suitcase and I live in it on vacation.”  